Text: Out of officeI will be out of the office for the rest of the week and will return on Monday Irena will be here should you need anything Have a great weekend everyone Alex Villarreal

REhi i like it here too i dont like that there are people behind me but i like the atmosphere pretty cool yeah its pretty warm in here not enough drawer space guess i will just have to get rid of a few things you didnt have to buy me anything but thanks for thinking of me its not the picture of the monkey holding the snake again is it ha ha jk hope you have a good day Original Message From Griffith John Sent Monday November AM To Villarreal Alex Subject Good morning how are you Quite a change huh I like it here The only problem is the heat from the monitors The heat My god the heat a Seinfeld episode Anyway I like it over here Really nice How do you like you new space is it okay I like being able to peak over and see you The table has turned You have to get up and look back to see me now Ha I bought you something small this weekend I will give it to you later It is nothing that important but I thought it was cute Oh well I guess I better work Have a great day and I hope to talk to you later John

REgo to programs system utility apps and then msn messenger Original Message From Griffith John Sent Monday November AM To Villarreal Alex Subject RE how Original Message From Villarreal Alex Sent Monday November AM To Griffith John Subject turn on your instant messenger
turn on your instant messenger

REthat was nice of you thanks for the thought i think i am finally starting to cool off i hope you rested well last night i am sorry that you have been feeling a little down i hope that you feel better today hey question would you be willing to move to another city Original Message From Griffith John Sent Monday November AM To Villarreal Alex Subject RE you guessed it I bought a really nice silver frame and everything I superimposed your face on the lady is that okay I am going to send it around the internet jk No it is something small Original Message From Villarreal Alex Sent Monday November AM To Griffith John Subject RE hi i like it here too i dont like that there are people behind me but i like the atmosphere pretty cool yeah its pretty warm in here not enough drawer space guess i will just have to get rid of a few things you didnt have to buy me anything but thanks for thinking of me its not the picture of the monkey holding the snake again is it ha ha jk hope you have a good day Original Message From Griffith John Sent Monday November AM To Villarreal Alex Subject Good morning how are you Quite a change huh I like it here The only problem is the heat from the monitors The heat My god the heat a Seinfeld episode Anyway I like it over here Really nice How do you like you new space is it okay I like being able to peak over and see you The table has turned You have to get up and look back to see me now Ha I bought you something small this weekend I will give it to you later It is nothing that important but I thought it was cute Oh well I guess I better work Have a great day and I hope to talk to you later John

RE Collection for Ebaythe drawings are really awesome but the real thing looks a little i dont know different in my opinion i think she should have used a different fabric something not as bold as this one Original Message From Griffith John Sent Monday November AM To Villarreal Alex Subject FW Collection for Ebay Here are some dresses that Elenas friend designed what do you think John Original Message From Chilkina Elena Sent Wednesday November AM To Griffith John Subject Collection for Ebay John Attached are photo and drawing of my friends collection she was looking to sell it through Ebay Maybe you could suggest the best way to put out there or could help her selling it Thanks Elena Elena E Chilkina Enron Americas Energy Risk Management
